0.01: New App!
0.02: Added accelerometer-based tremor detection
0.03: Fixed tremor false positives — switched to diff-based frequency counting
0.04: Fixed bug where sensitivity didn't affect tick counting, raised min thresholds
0.05: Raised HRM confidence threshold to 85%, require 2 stable readings, expire stale BPM after 10s
0.06: Default HR threshold 140, confidence 90, tremor detector much stricter
0.07: Rebalanced tremor thresholds — v0.06 was too strict, v0.04 too loose
0.08: Lowered count threshold and persistence for faster tremor response
0.09: Default tremor sensitivity lowered to 1
